## STOP! This repository is READ-ONLY

This repository is automatically synchronized from a private monorepo.

**Your pull request will NOT be merged.**

### What to do instead:

1. **For BSG team members:** Make changes in the private `bsg-sdk` repository
2. **For external contributors:** Please open an **Issue** instead, describing your suggestion or bug

### Why?

All code in this repository is auto-generated from OpenAPI specifications. Manual changes would be overwritten on the next release.
